<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>TKA Matematika Interaktif</title>

<style>
body {
    font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    background: #f4f6f8;
    margin: 30px;
}
.container {
    background: #fff;
    padding: 25px;
    border-radius: 10px;
    box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
}
h1 {
    color: #1a73e8;
}
.soal {
    margin-bottom: 30px;
}
.opsi button {
    display: block;
    margin: 5px 0;
    padding: 10px;
    width: 100%;
    border: none;
    border-radius: 6px;
    background: #e3eafc;
    cursor: pointer;
    text-align: left;
}
.opsi button:hover {
    background: #c6dafc;
}
.benar {
    background: #c8f7c5 !important;
}
.salah {
    background: #f7c5c5 !important;
}
.pembahasan {
    display: none;
    background: #eef3ff;
    padding: 10px;
    border-radius: 6px;
    margin-top: 10px;
}
</style>

<script>
function cekJawaban(btn, benar, pembahasanId) {
    let buttons = btn.parentElement.querySelectorAll("button");
    buttons.forEach(b => b.disabled = true);

    if (btn.getAttribute("data-jawaban") === benar) {
        btn.classList.add("benar");
    } else {
        btn.classList.add("salah");
    }

    document.getElementById(pembahasanId).style.display = "block";
}
</script>

</head>
<body>

<div class="container">
<h1>📘 TKA Matematika (Literasi & Numerasi)</h1>

<!-- SOAL 1 -->
<div class="soal">
<p><b>1.</b> Harga beras naik dari Rp10.000 menjadi Rp12.500. Persentase kenaikan adalah...</p>
<div class="opsi">
<button onclick="cekJawaban(this,'B','p1')" data-jawaban="A">A. 20%</button>
<button onclick="cekJawaban(this,'B','p1')" data-jawaban="B">B. 25%</button>
<button onclick="cekJawaban(this,'B','p1')" data-jawaban="C">C. 30%</button>
<button onclick="cekJawaban(this,'B','p1')" data-jawaban="D">D. 35%</button>
<button onclick="cekJawaban(this,'B','p1')" data-jawaban="E">E. 40%</button>
</div>
<div id="p1" class="pembahasan">
Kenaikan = 2.500 → (2500/10000) × 100% = 25%
</div>
</div>

<!-- SOAL 2 -->
<div class="soal">
<p><b>2.</b> Jumlah pengunjung naik dari 200 ke 260. Persentase kenaikan adalah...</p>
<div class="opsi">
<button onclick="cekJawaban(this,'C','p2')" data-jawaban="A">A. 20%</button>
<button onclick="cekJawaban(this,'C','p2')" data-jawaban="B">B. 25%</button>
<button onclick="cekJawaban(this,'C','p2')" data-jawaban="C">C. 30%</button>
<button onclick="cekJawaban(this,'C','p2')" data-jawaban="D">D. 35%</button>
<button onclick="cekJawaban(this,'C','p2')" data-jawaban="E">E. 40%</button>
</div>
<div id="p2" class="pembahasan">
Kenaikan = 60 → (60/200) × 100% = 30%
</div>
</div>

<!-- SOAL 3 -->
<div class="soal">
<p><b>3.</b> 60% dari 200 siswa menyukai matematika. Yang tidak menyukai adalah...</p>
<div class="opsi">
<button onclick="cekJawaban(this,'D','p3')" data-jawaban="A">A. 60</button>
<button onclick="cekJawaban(this,'D','p3')" data-jawaban="B">B. 70</button>
<button onclick="cekJawaban(this,'D','p3')" data-jawaban="C">C. 75</button>
<button onclick="cekJawaban(this,'D','p3')" data-jawaban="D">D. 80</button>
<button onclick="cekJawaban(this,'D','p3')" data-jawaban="E">E. 90</button>
</div>
<div id="p3" class="pembahasan">
Tidak suka = 40% × 200 = 80
</div>
</div>

<!-- SOAL 4 -->
<div class="soal">
<p><b>4.</b> Seorang pekerja menyelesaikan 3/4 pekerjaan dalam 6 jam. Waktu total pekerjaan adalah...</p>
<div class="opsi">
<button onclick="cekJawaban(this,'B','p4')" data-jawaban="A">A. 6 jam</button>
<button onclick="cekJawaban(this,'B','p4')" data-jawaban="B">B. 8 jam</button>
<button onclick="cekJawaban(this,'B','p4')" data-jawaban="C">C. 9 jam</button>
<button onclick="cekJawaban(this,'B','p4')" data-jawaban="D">D. 10 jam</button>
<button onclick="cekJawaban(this,'B','p4')" data-jawaban="E">E. 12 jam</button>
</div>
<div id="p4" class="pembahasan">
1 pekerjaan = 6 ÷ (3/4) = 8 jam
</div>
</div>

<!-- SOAL 5 -->
<div class="soal">
<p><b>5.</b> Harga Rp100.000 didiskon 10% lalu 20%. Harga akhir adalah...</p>
<div class="opsi">
<button onclick="cekJawaban(this,'C','p5')" data-jawaban="A">A. 70.000</button>
<button onclick="cekJawaban(this,'C','p5')" data-jawaban="B">B. 72.000</button>
<button onclick="cekJawaban(this,'C','p5')" data-jawaban="C">C. 72.000</button>
<button onclick="cekJawaban(this,'C','p5')" data-jawaban="D">D. 75.000</button>
<button onclick="cekJawaban(this,'C','p5')" data-jawaban="E">E. 80.000</button>
</div>
<div id="p5" class="pembahasan">
100.000 → diskon 10% = 90.000 → diskon 20% = 72.000
</div>
</div>

</div>

</body>
</html>
